{
  "stem": "3721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But sometimes, in the middle of August, we noticed that the-- moving, movement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Germans moved on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we figured that the Russians must be very near because we heard the artillery shells exploding already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we figured we'd get out, and somewhere we'd hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, and we'll be-- we'll survive that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Anyway, it took us about three, four days that we removed enough huge rocks from the foundation, so we could somehow get through.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the-- this Ilona was a little stockier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To get her through was a little more difficult than getting me through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was quite skinny at the time, OK?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was the first one to be out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went and looked around, if I-- we see anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I went for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I sort of whispered to get them out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because during the day, we still heard soldiers going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although we knew they, they moved-- but we didn't know if they had any guards or didn't have any guards.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we got all the three people out, I was the first one to sort of like a scout, seeing if there are any guard.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wanted to go up to the mountain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In our hometown, they had a lot of vineyards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I figured if I go up to the-- to the top of the mountain, we'll be able to feed ourselves with water and, and grapes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because that was the-- the end of August is already the grape season.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "However, I got out, and I saw nobody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the other three made too much noise.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a Hungarian guard came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all the men-- with the rifles shaking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I kept on saying, run.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
